        <IsA>app:console</IsA>
        <Summary>An accompaniment generator--it creates midi tracks for a soloist to perform over from a user supplied file containing chords and MMA directives.</Summary>
        <Description>MMA is very versatile and generates excellent tracks. It comes with an extensive user-extendable library with a variety of patterns for various popular rhythms, detailed user manuals, and several demo songs. MMA is a command line driven program. It creates MIDI files which are then played by a sequencer or MIDI file play program. </Description>
